description:
Rick Stein: From Venice to Istanbul - Series 1, Episode 7




Istanbul

Rick Stein's culinary odyssey has brought him from historic Venice to the legendary city of Istanbul, where he arrives in time for the bluefish season and catches a few himself while fishing on the Bosphorus. A friend invites him for a home cooked lunch of bulgur pilaf with chicken and he cooks lavish kofte kebabs with pistachios and the much-loved Black Sea dish kapuska.




Original Air Date: 18-Sep-2015
